                  <join result="offencePlace" targOrder="Y" targets="t18290910-133-off750 t18290910-133-crimeloc752"></join>, about three o'clock in the morning; I felt my handkerchief taken, turned and saw the prisoner behind me; he ran off; I chased him, and caught him - he threw down the handkerchief, and I took it up; this is it.</p>
               <p>
                  <xptr type="pageFacsimile" doc="182909100069"></xptr>Prisoner. Q. Did you see me throw it down? A. Yes - there was no young woman with me.</p>
